query:
SELECT l.id, l.nome, gl.gestorId
FROM lojas l
JOIN gestor_lojas gl ON l.id = gl.lojaId
JOIN gestores g ON gl.gestorId = g.id
JOIN users u ON g.userId = u.id
WHERE u.name LIKE '%Marco Amorim%'
ORDER BY l.nome;
